'''Fury Squadron''' was a [[Toscan 8-Q starfighter|Toscan 8-Q]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Squadron/Legends|squadron]] operated by a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] group in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]].

Shortly before the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]], Fury Squadron and [[Pirate Squadron]] accompanied [[Marauder-class Assault Corvette/Legends|Marauder-class corvette]] [[Vulture (Marauder-class)|''Vulture'']] on a raid against [[Casino/Legends|casino]] owner [[Dunari]]. Unfortunately, Dunari was defended by [[Z-95 Headhunter/Legends|Z-95 Headhunters]] of [[Bandit Squadron]] from the [[Mon Calamari Star Cruiser/Legends|Mon Calamari Star Cruiser]] [[Liberty/Legends|''Liberty'']], who fought off the pirates and inflicted heavy losses.

